{"tid":1942102,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】俄羅斯官媒引科學家稱　武肺病毒或來自外太空　隨隕石墜落中國　被批偽科學","createTime":"2020-03-25T00:28:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-25T13:29:41.000Z","uid":80516,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"94854bd4de211f0db090a15d85861ff8c2e4cdeb","tid":1942102,"uid":80516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T00:28:11.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎疫情在全球蔓延，病毒源頭已演變成一場國際外交風波。一名英國科學家近日作出驚人的推斷，聲稱病毒可能來自外太空，隨隕石墮落中國，俄羅斯官媒《俄羅斯衛星通訊社》在微博發表相關報道，更引述一名俄羅斯醫學專家稱認同這說法，報道隨即被不少大陸媒體轉載、引用；不過這個說法很快被不少科學家質疑欠缺足夠證明，只是「偽科學」。<br />\n<br />\n《俄羅斯衛星通訊社》昨日發表報道，指英國威爾斯卡迪夫大學的外太空生物學家 Chandra Wickramasinghe 稱，武漢肺炎病毒可能來自太空，隨著去年 10 月在中國上空爆炸的隕石墜落地球，報道又指俄羅斯科學院生物醫學問題研究所主任維亞切斯拉夫&middot;伊利英，亦認同這說法。<br />\n<br />\n其實 Wickramasinghe 並非首次發表外太空病毒的概念。早在 2005 年，他亦提出 SARS 病毒是來自外太空，不過這些說法都未獲科學界普遍認同。在今次武漢肺炎疫情出現後，Wickramasinghe 再次接受媒體訪問，提出外太空病毒一說。<br />\n<br />\n美國太空總署天體生物學研究所的宇宙生物學家 Graham Lau 反駁，若果病毒可以在太空幅射下生存，在墜落地球後仍然有能力感染人類，這將會是史無前例的大發現，但目前根本沒有足夠理據支持這說法，「我認為作為科學家，有必要指出偽科學及壞科學（bad science）」。<br />\n<br />\nGraham Lau 又指，新型冠狀病毒結構與其他地球上已知的病毒相似，除非病毒有某種不同於人類理解的生物分子，否則沒有理由懷疑病毒來自地球之外。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gaRs05A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgaRs05A.png&h=4cb4af43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/武漢肺炎-俄羅斯官媒引科學家稱-武肺病毒或來自外太空-隨隕石墜落中國-被批偽科學/?fbclid=IwAR1p3lR-OrezX8lK1DNlRnkzWsrzwnoHHXSfUflVoFlCuudcPAgsYiK_iL0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E5%AE%98%E5%AA%92%E5%BC%95%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%B8%E5%AE%B6%E7%A8%B1-%E6%AD%A6%E8%82%BA%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E6%88%96%E4%BE%86%E8%87%AA%E5%A4%96%E5%A4%AA%E7%A9%BA-%E9%9A%A8%E9%9A%95%E7%9F%B3%E5%A2%9C%E8%90%BD%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E8%A2%AB%E6%89%B9%E5%81%BD%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%B8%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1p3lR-OrezX8lK1DNlRnkzWsrzwnoHHXSfUflVoFlCuudcPAgsYiK_iL0&d=D0cCki4bmudO7bhudq%2Bynxfhc2i76iEVsdTpjF8%2BTp8%3D&h=5e0b372b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E5%AE%98%E5%AA%92%E5%BC%95%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%B8%E5%AE%B6%E7%A8%B1-%E6%AD%A6%E8%82%BA%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E6%88%96%E4%BE%86%E8%87%AA%E5%A4%96%E5%A4%AA%E7%A9%BA-%E9%9A%A8%E9%9A%95%E7%9F%B3%E5%A2%9C%E8%90%BD%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E8%A2%AB%E6%89%B9%E5%81%BD%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%B8%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1p3lR-OrezX8lK1DNlRnkzWsrzwnoHHXSfUflVoFlCuudcPAgsYiK_iL0&h=8baf381b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/武漢肺炎-俄羅斯官媒引科學家稱-武肺病毒或來自外太空-隨隕石墜落中國-被批偽科學/?fbclid=IwAR1p3lR-OrezX8lK1DNlRnkzWsrzwnoHHXSfUflVoFlCuudcPAgsYiK_iL0</a>"},{"pid":"12a386660d913dd4cb9c91cd4eb315ab52ce4a0b","tid":1942102,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T00:31:28.000Z","msg":"聽講舊隕石仲帶左一隻叫異形嘅生物落嚟呀<br />\n<br />\n俄佬睇戲太多"},{"pid":"47959b8d25aacee261efcaf4333c9df92a386d76","tid":1942102,"uid":129878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T01:04:23.000Z","msg":"有智力都知高温會殺死病毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19411aca2bc892563b407f025ad46121788afbe5","tid":1942102,"uid":192409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T01:05:23.000Z","msg":"屌你衛斯理寫科幻小說咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b576b076ac352940caf7c500b9e66747030ffc7","tid":1942102,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T01:05:34.000Z","msg":"外星人要佔領地球，所以用病毒殺哂全世界人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eb55ee